      🚀 Production Pipeline

      Complete workflow now available:

      # 1. Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt
pre-commit install

# 2. Run tests
pytest --cov=.

# 3. Generate prompt
python prompt_generator.py --config element.yaml --output prompt.xml

# 4. Validate prompt
python asset_validator.py --prompt prompt.xml

# 5. Generate image
python nano_banana_integration.py --prompt prompt.xml --output assets/generated/

# 6. Validate layout
python asset_validator.py --layout config/layouts/spread_04_05.yaml

# 7. Compose spread
python klutz_compositor.py config/layouts/spread_04_05.yaml output/spread.png

# 8. Post-process
python post_processor.py --input output/spread.png --output output/final.png

# 9. QA check
python quality_assurance.py --spread output/final.png --report

## IMPLEMENTATION DETAILS

### Asset Validator (Period Police)
- 65 forbidden design terms (gradient, flat design, mobile, etc.)
- 14 allowed modern terms (aseprite, layer, export, etc.)
- Required visual terms for hardware/software depiction
- Color distribution validation (70/20/10 rule)
- Spine intrusion detection (dead zone 1469-1931px)
- Rotation limits (text ≤5°, containers ≤15°, photos ≤10°)
- Safe zone validation (100px margins)
- CLI with exit codes for automation

### Klutz Compositor
- Deterministic "chaos" rotation using MD5 hash
- Paper texture generation with NumPy noise
- 4:1 pitch spiral binding (57px holes, 18px spacing)
- Page curvature simulation with quadratic shadow falloff
- Asset loading with rotation, border, and shadow
- Programmatic text rendering with word wrapping
- CMYK misregistration (+1px magenta, -1px yellow)
- Dot gain simulation (gamma 0.95)
- Vignette effect with radial gradient
- CLI with --no-artifacts and --verbose flags

### AI Integration
- Prompt generator with 6 built-in templates
- Gemini client with caching, rate limiting, retry logic
- nano-banana client with parallel generation, progress tracking
- Post-processor with texture, CMYK shift, dot gain, vignette
- Quality assurance with color distribution, text legibility, authenticity checks

### Testing
- 213 tests across 8 test files
- Mock API clients (Gemini, nano-banana)
- Image comparison utilities
- Custom pytest fixtures
- Performance benchmarks (< 30s per spread)
- Integration tests for full pipeline
- 80%+ coverage target
